(136, 1, '2024-11-07 14:13:33', '2024-11-07 14:13:33', '<h2>About Us</h2>		\n		<h4>   Our Roots In Kindness</h4><h4>       (Origin Story)</h4><p>Kindness is at the heart of everything we do  but  were about so much more. With the aim of creating skincare that is fuss-free and approachable, were committed to keeping you and your skin looking (and feeling!) its best, starting with clean, uncomplicated products that downright love your skin and the planet too.</p><p>What is clean beauty, you ask? It is saying a big NO to baddies such as perfume/fragrance, colours, etc known to upset your skin, because what we leave out is just as important as what we put in.</p><p>Whats even more amazing is that Simple has been in the clean beauty game way before it was cool!</p><p>Our free-from list boasts more than 2000 harsh chemicals that are harmful to your skin! But we dont stop there, we are committed to clean beauty and for that, every year 10% of our profits go towards R&amp;D. These efforts are to further work on our free-from list and increase the number of blacklisted ingredients. Oh yes, we take a lot of pride in this ever-increasing list!</p>		\n						<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-4390\" open>\n				<summary data-accordion-index=\"1\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-4390\" >\n					<h5> Our Misson </h5>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n						</summary>\n							<p>Our mission is to empower individuals to achieve healthy, radiant skin through innovative, natural, and scientifically proven solutions. We are committed to sustainability, inclusivity, and creating products that enhance confidence while nurturing the planet.</p>						\n					</details>\n						<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-4391\" >\n				<summary data-accordion-index=\"2\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-4391\" >\n					<h5> Our  Vision </h5>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n						</summary>\n							<p>Our vision is to be a global leader in skincare, setting new standards for quality, innovation, and sustainability. We strive to inspire a world where everyone feels confident in their own skin, fostering beauty, well-being, and self-love for all.</p>						\n					</details>\n						<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-4392\" >\n				<summary data-accordion-index=\"3\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-4392\" >\n					<h5> Our Core Values </h5>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n			<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"></path></svg>\n						</summary>\n							<ul><li><strong>Quality</strong>  Commitment to creating safe, effective, and high-performing products.</li><li><strong>Integrity</strong>  Transparency in our ingredients, processes, and promises.</li><li><strong>Innovation</strong>  Leveraging science and nature to deliver cutting-edge skincare solutions.</li><li><strong>Sustainability</strong>  Prioritizing eco-friendly practices and reducing our environmental impact.</li><li><strong>Inclusivity</strong>  Celebrating diverse skin types and tones, ensuring every product meets the needs of all.</li><li><strong>Customer-Centric</strong>  Listening to our customers to continually improve and meet their expectations.</li><li><strong>Empowerment</strong>  Encouraging confidence and self-love through healthier, radiant skin.</li></ul>						\n					</details>\n		<p>Our mission is to empower individuals to achieve healthy, radiant skin through innovative, natural, and scientifically proven solutions. We are committed to sustainability, inclusivity, and creating products that enhance confidence while nurturing the planet.</p><p>Our vision is to be a global leader in skincare, setting new standards for quality, innovation, and sustainability. We strive to inspire a world where everyone feels confident in their own skin, fostering beauty, well-being, and self-love for all.</p><ul><li><strong>Quality</strong>  Commitment to creating safe, effective, and high-performing products.</li><li><strong>Integrity</strong>  Transparency in our ingredients, processes, and promises.</li><li><strong>Innovation</strong>  Leveraging science and nature to deliver cutting-edge skincare solutions.</li><li><strong>Sustainability</strong>  Prioritizing eco-friendly practices and reducing our environmental impact.</li><li><strong>Inclusivity</strong>  Celebrating diverse skin types and tones, ensuring every product meets the needs of all.</li><li><strong>Customer-Centric</strong>  Listening to our customers to continually improve and meet their expectations.</li><li><strong>Empowerment</strong>  Encouraging confidence and self-love through healthier, radiant skin.</li></ul>		\n			<h2>OUR TEAM</h2>		\n				<figure>\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG_0977.jpg\" alt=\"Ilu Dangol\">\n				</figure>\n				<h2>Ilu Dangol</h2>\n				<h3>Full Stack Developer</h3>\n															<ul>\n																																									<li>\n										<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/p/Sarika-Dangol-100028033967682/\" target=\"_blank\">\n																							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M504 256C504 119 393 8 256 8S8 119 8 256c0 123.78 90.69 226.38 209.25 245V327.69h-63V256h63v-54.64c0-62.15 37-96.48 93.67-96.48 27.14 0 55.52 4.84 55.52 4.84v61h-31.28c-30.8 0-40.41 19.12-40.41 38.73V256h68.78l-11 71.69h-57.78V501C413.31 482.38 504 379.78 504 256z\"></path></svg>																					</a>\n									</li>\n																																																	<li>\n										<a target=\"_blank\">\n																							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M459.37 151.716c.325 4.548.325 9.097.325 13.645 0 138.72-105.583 298.558-298.558 298.558-59.452 0-114.68-17.219-161.137-47.106 8.447.974 16.568 1.299 25.34 1.299 49.055 0 94.213-16.568 130.274-44.832-46.132-.975-84.792-31.188-98.112-72.772 6.498.974 12.995 1.624 19.818 1.624 9.421 0 18.843-1.3 27.614-3.573-48.081-9.747-84.143-51.98-84.143-102.985v-1.299c13.969 7.797 30.214 12.67 47.431 13.319-28.264-18.843-46.781-51.005-46.781-87.391 0-19.492 5.197-37.36 14.294-52.954 51.655 63.675 129.3 105.258 216.365 109.807-1.624-7.797-2.599-15.918-2.599-24.04 0-57.828 46.782-104.934 104.934-104.934 30.213 0 57.502 12.67 76.67 33.137 23.71