(190, 1, '2024-11-07 18:59:19', '2024-11-07 18:59:19', 'This salicylic acid toner for acne-prone skin works as a whitehead & blackhead remover, decongests skin pores and regulates sebum production. The face toner removes excess oil from the face, limiting further outbreaks. This pore-tightening toner keeps the skin hydrated while eradicating acne-causing bacteria.The presence of Tea tree oil\'s anti-inflammatory properties in this face toner for oily skin, treats acne inflammation, reducing acne redness, swelling, itching, and burning sensations.The antibacterial properties of neem leaf extract, present in this toner for acne-prone skin, treat all types of comedonal acne and relieve irritated skin. The salicylic acid face toner reduces early ageing signs, lightens acne scars, and promotes uniform skin tone.\r\n\r\n', 'Teenilicious Acne Face Toner With Salicylic Acid-100 Ml', 'Teenilicious Acne Face Toner With Salicylic Acid & Tea Tree Oil is a deep-level pore clearing formulation. Neem Leaf Extract works as a skin calming agent. This mild toner effectively tackles congested pores, blackheads, breakouts, and other acne-related concerns', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'teenilicious-acne-face-toner-with-salicylic-acid-100-ml', '', '', '2024-12-09 10:04:41', '2024-12-09 10:04:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=190', 0, 'product', '', 0),
